        <!-- SLIDE 1: Title -->
        <div class="slide active">
            <h1>Learning From Complex Cases</h1>
            <h2>Diagnostic Reasoning in Hospital Medicine</h2>
            
            <div class="content-section" style="margin-top: 40px;">
                <h3>Case Presentation: 82-Year-Old Male with Recurrent Pneumonia</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2em; margin-top: 20px;">
                    A teaching case demonstrating the importance of comprehensive chart review, 
                    diagnostic reasoning, and care coordination
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="learning-point" style="margin-top: 40px;">
                <h3>Learning Objectives</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Develop systematic approaches to comprehensive chart review</li>
                    <li>Recognize infection risk in chronic lymphoproliferative disorders</li>
                    <li>Apply clinical reasoning when laboratory and clinical findings diverge</li>
                    <li>Implement antibiotic stewardship principles in complex patients</li>
                    <li>Identify system-level opportunities for quality improvement</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.1em;"><strong>Note:</strong> This is a real case with identifying information removed. 
                The focus is on learning and systems improvement, not individual performance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 2: Chief Complaint & Presentation -->
        <div class="slide">
            <h1>Initial Presentation</h1>
            
            <div class="content-section">
                <h3>Chief Complaint</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: bold;">"Altered mental status, breathing problem"</p>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">First Admission (Day -8)</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Neighbor found patient confused and short of breath</li>
                        <li>Symptoms present for several days</li>
                        <li>Patient unable to provide reliable history (dementia)</li>
                        <li>Chest X-ray: Bibasilar opacities</li>
                        <li>Started IV antibiotics, clinical improvement</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">Hospital Day 5</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Left Against Medical Advice</strong></li>
                        <li>Was alert and oriented × 3, had capacity</li>
                        <li>Family wanted long-term care placement</li>
                        <li>Patient refused: "I was tired of being in the hospital"</li>
                        <li>Discharged on oral antibiotics</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">48 Hours Later</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Re-presentation</strong></li>
                        <li>Neighbors found patient somnolent</li>
                        <li>SpO2 84% on room air</li>
                        <li>Initially hypotensive (BP 65/45)</li>
                        <li>Transferred to our facility</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="critical-box">
                <p><strong>Key Context:</strong> Patient lives alone, progressive dementia, medication non-compliance, 
                still driving despite cognitive impairment</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 3: Past Medical History -->
        <div class="slide">
            <h1>Past Medical History</h1>
            
            <div class="two-column">
                <div class="content-section">
                    <h3>Documented in Admission H&P</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Vascular dementia (progressive)</li>
                        <li>Myasthenia gravis</li>
                        <li>CKD Stage 4 (baseline unclear)</li>
                        <li>Hypertension</li>
                        <li>Hyperlipidemia</li>
                        <li>GERD</li>
                        <li>Depression/Mood disorder</li>
                        <li>Peripheral neuropathy</li>
                        <li>Restless legs syndrome</li>
                        <li>BPH</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h3>Medications (25 total)</h3>
                        <ul style="font-size: 0.95em;">
                            <li>Pyridostigmine (myasthenia)</li>
                            <li>Memantine (dementia)</li>
                            <li>Multiple psych medications</li>
                            <li>Losartan (held)</li>
                            <li>Pravastatin</li>
                            <li>Ferrous sulfate</li>
                            <li>Gabapentin (adjusted for renal function)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="critical-box" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                        <h3>Notable Medication Absences</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><span class="crossmark">✗</span> NO prophylactic antibiotics</li>
                            <li><span class="crossmark">✗</span> NO antivirals</li>
                            <li><span class="crossmark">✗</span> NO IVIG</li>
                            <li><span class="crossmark">✗</span> NO chemotherapy agents</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <p><strong>Clinical Question:</strong> Does this medication list match the documented problem list? 
                What might be missing?</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 4: Vital Signs & Physical Exam -->
        <div class="slide">
