            <div class="two-column" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <div class="content-section">
                    <h3>Physical Exam Highlights</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>General:</strong> Alert, no acute distress</li>
                        <li><strong>Lungs:</strong> Rhonchorous breath sounds over left base</li>
                        <li><strong>Cardiovascular:</strong> RRR, no murmurs</li>
                        <li><strong>Neurological:</strong> A&O × 3, but "not fully alert to situation"</li>
                        <li><strong>Extremities:</strong> No edema</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Physical Exam Considerations</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Were lymph nodes examined?</li>
                        <li>Was hepatosplenomegaly assessed?</li>
                        <li>Complete exam documentation important</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

